description: Location, location, location! With summer around the corner you do not want to miss this sun soaked penthouse unit with not one but TWO private outdoor spaces. This home features open concept living, two bedrooms, a bathroom complete with a tile & glassed in shower and washer/dryer in unit. Dark stained floors, stainless steel appliances, custom built out closets and blinds, and surround sound are just icing on the cake here. The real wow factor with in this home is the amazing private 271SF roof deck with sweeping city views. Situated on a quiet one way alley street, this home just steps away from all that West Broadway and South Boston have to offer- shops, cafes fitness studios and restaurants. Easy highway and MBTA access. If you have been dreaming of the Southie lifestyle this one is IT.
